"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-football-paris-2024-olympics-football-draw-in-full-usa-france-b1146656.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Football  The draw for the 2024Paris Olympicshas been made for both the men's and women's tournaments.  Emma Hayeswill lead theUSAout at her first international tournament against Germany, Australia and one of Zambia and Morocco in Group B.  Team GB did not qualify and Group C pits World Cup winners Spain against Brazil.  In the men's game, hosts France have been drawn against the USA, either South Africa, Nigeria, Zambia or Guinea and New Zealand.  Women'sOlympic FootballTournament  Group A: France, Colombia, Canada, New Zealand  Group B: USA, CAF 2 (Zambia or Morocco), Germany, Australia  Group C: Spain, Japan, CAF 1 (Nigeria or Morocco), Brazil  Men's Olympic Football Tournament  Group A: France, USA, AFC 4 or Guinea, New Zealand  Group B: Argentina, Morocco, AFC 3, Ukraine  Group C:AFC 2, Spain, Egypt, Dominican Republic  Group D: AFC 1, Paraguay, Mali, Israel  Group games for both tournaments begin on Wednesday July 24, 2024.  The men's final is scheduled for Friday August 9 and the women's for Saturday August 10.  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\"}"